  greedComplete: 0
  greedStoryDone: 0
  greedCharacterLines:
  - Congratulations! How was the Greed Trial?
  - It was... interesting.
  - I was instructed to grab coins falling from the sky.
  - 'Ah, classic Greed at its core. '
  - It felt... wrong though.
  - Don't fight the feeling, Isabel! Sometimes, it can be a lesson for you!
  - Your friend, Diego... he's hospitalized right now, isn't he?
  - 'Yeah... '
  - And I presume those medical bills must be extremely high, huh?
  - That... that is correct...
  - See, in order to save your friend, Diego, you have to pay a hefty price for him
    to get treatment!
  - When we get out of here, you're going to have to do more than just use your own
    savings to pay for Diego's hospital bills.
  - Wha-what do you mean?
  - There's no other way around it, dear Isabel. You know what you have to do.
  - ...
  - You mean... steal people's money?
  - 'Unfortunately... yes. More than that: rob banks too. It is sinful, I know. But
    I promised I would help you heal Diego.'
  - This is one way we're going to do it.
