  wrathComplete: 0
  wrathStoryDone: 0
  wrathCharacterLines:
  - You've passed the Wrath Trial! How do you feel?
  - I feel... energized? Stronger?
  - What about your anger? How did it feel to let it all out?
  - I... I didn't feel anger. Wha-what are you talking about?
  - Isabel... what's wrong?
  - ...
  - I know you got anger inside you. Anger from being the cause of your friend's
    dire situation, huh?
  - ...
  - Feeling guilty about it, huh? Beating yourself up over it?
  - It was my idea to split up in the ancient ruins. I did it so we could cover more
    ground.
  - Now... looking back on it...
  - You believe it was your fault, don't you?
  - ...
  - Let it all out, Isabel. Stomp the ground, punch anything and everything around
    you!
  - Let out your wrath, as the Wrath Trial taught you!
  - UGHHH!!
  - 'I... I... '
  - '*stomps the ground*'
  - '*screams*'
  - '*aggressively throws a nearby rock into the wall*'
  - Atta, girl. And maybe... just maybe... you'll realize that you do not need to
    carry this weight on your shoulders anymore...
