  prideComplete: 0
  prideStoryDone: 0
  prideCharacterLines:
  - DIEGO!
  - ISABEL!
  - '*hug*'
  - Diego... you're all better!
  - I... I guess I am!
  - Escaping Lucifer's Trial room must've worked some magic on my body or something.
  - Let's get out of here, Diego. I cannot stand another moment of being in this
    Hellhole.
  - Haha, I agree. Let's go.
  - '*The two friends then exit through a portal created from beating Lucifer''s
    Trial*'
  - '*With that, they teleported back to the real world, ready for their next archaeologist
    expedition*'
  - '*This time, being sure to stick close together... and, of course, never reading
    from an ancient cursed book again*'
  - '*THE END!*'
